---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Mårten Wikman">
  <article class="about">
    <header class="reveal">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="reveal">
      <h2 class="mono-label section-label">Profile</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          I work at the intersection of finance and data. My academic grounding
          is in strategic management and international business; my practical
          toolkit is SQL, Python, Power BI, and data modeling. That combination
          means I can build the analysis myself — from raw data to a defensible
          valuation or market view — rather than waiting on someone else's
          spreadsheet.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm targeting roles in private equity, M&amp;A advisory, and growth
          consulting, where that hybrid profile does its best work: commercial
          questions answered with real data discipline.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="reveal">
      <h2 class="mono-label section-label">Dissertation</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          My dissertation examined cross-border post-merger integration through
          Simons' four levers of control — how acquirers balance belief systems,
          boundary systems, diagnostic controls, and interactive controls when
          integrating a foreign target. It received a <strong>First Class</strong>{" "}
          grade and anchors the{" "}
          <a href="/work/post-merger-integration/">Post-Merger Integration</a>{" "}
          section of this portfolio.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="reveal">
      <h2 class="mono-label section-label">Education</h2>
      <ul class="edu-list" role="list">
        <li>
          <span class="edu-title">BSc International Business Management</span>
          <span class="mono edu-meta">Coventry University</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="edu-title">Business Intelligence Analyst</span>
          <span class="mono edu-meta">Nackademin — Swedish pathway</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="reveal">
      <h2 class="mono-label section-label">Contact</h2>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          <a href="mailto:marten@wikman.se" class="mono">marten@wikman.se</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 46rem;
  }

  .about section {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline);
  }

  .section-label {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .edu-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .edu-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .edu-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .edu-meta {
    color: var(--fog);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }
</style>
